<author>bytr wyṣạ, bytr wyṣạ</author>
<lyrics>[V1]
 1- qad̊ kẖalaq̊ta rabĩy jasadī lidẖā sẖakẖĩṣ̊ ạản̊ta maraḍī
 fabiwajaʿiy ạản̊ta ạảd̊ray̱
 wibisaqamiy las̊ta tar̊ḍay̱
 ạlqrạr- ạản̊ta sẖifāʾuⁿ lkulĩ ạảd̊wāyỉy min̊ka ạảl̊qay̱ rabĩy dawāyỉy
 ạản̊ta maẘlạaya kẖabīruⁿ
 faqad̊ nasajat̊ yaduka ạảḥ̊sẖāyỉy
 2- kawãn̊ta tafāṣīla jis̊mī
 ạảb̊daʿat̊ rīsẖatuka ras̊mī
 haạka kulĩy ạảnā ladaẙka ạảr̊jū masãẗa yadaẙka
 3- las̊tu ạảs̊tanidu bibasẖariⁿ las̊tu ạảtãsimu bifasẖaliⁿ
 wātẖiquⁿ fīka ṭabībiy
 mun̊qidẖī jur̊ḥu ạlṣãlībi</lyrics>
<title>ạ̉bdʿt rysẖtk rsmy</title>
</song>